race.description: Kembla Classic Race Day March 13Th Maiden Plate
race.comment: MAREBELLO (1) lightly raced four-year-old with a stack of upside. Finds his race third-up after being nailed late when second in a small field over 1600m at Gosford. Has the pace to slide across from the draw and near his top now. Go close. EUREKA REBEL (6) went back from the draw and ran below expectations when a plugging eighth over this track and trip in a Super Maiden. Can race a little closer from the inside draw and assess on his good debut placing. WILLIE OR WONG HE (10) up in trip at his second career start when an even fifth over 1600m at Gosford. Will relish the claim and expected to improve. VALENTIAGO (8) jumps in class and shouldn't be a Maiden for long. Dropped back a few grades when a fast finishing second over 1400m at Bathurst. Set to peak and has placed at this track and trip. Each-way.
